{"id": "1262070392735137845", "channel_id": "1261996471469871125", "type": 0, "author_id": "1139928180254326927", "author_name": "rock1234_47882", "author_bot": false, "content": "你是谁，牢暮应该是说没有12+12不能玩的人", "timestamp": "2024-07-14T15:37:09.762000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1261996471469871125", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海米粒至高毒队攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1174179680056791130", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1262078963778457712", "channel_id": "1261996471469871125", "type": 0, "author_id": "1247534528709398553", "author_name": "sylvestre.01", "author_bot": false, "content": "你是谁，牢暮应该是说没有12+12不能玩的人", "timestamp": "2024-07-14T16:11:13.258000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1261996471469871125", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "深海米粒至高毒队攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1174179680056791130", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1262001903907373147", "channel_id": "1262001903907373147", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "（思路仅供参考，不一定完全正确）\n         首先是第一关，这关时灵摆最关键的是爆死扛给盾，所以我用的是盾击队，然后女仆和24都是可以替换成自己box里面的剩余角色。获胜思路：苟活然后慢慢磨死。\n         第二关，时灵摆很常规，所以我在安排好345以后拿出了最喜欢的希洛莉莉去打，主要是为了让希洛有点出场率（校猫什么时候加强希洛？），实际上这关用水母打应该会很好打。\n         第三关，这个时灵摆就是国家队特供的，所以没什么好说的。\n         第四关，这关能抽卡然后弃牌给狂气，为了最大化利用这个狂气，我选混沌体系，四小只白送的+4超限，然后因为我box比较齐全，就带上了泥工的超高配24增加一下我的游戏体验，实际上那个位置换成自己的60级24或者换成超限的罗坦也是可以轻松过关的，如果觉得生存压力打，boss福袋的衍生卡是可以弃掉的。这关的唯一难点是需要注意一下进门后的第一个精英怪，如果不提前做好队伍的钥令和狂气的储备，会掉大量状态，甚至交出死扛。\n         第五关，我用的新鲜的+4红花，打的时候脑测一下如果是60的3+3红，可能会稍微有些吃力，如果你前面第二关是用的水母鲨鱼过关的话，这关神父可以扛起血肉大旗。\n\n总的来说，我这份375答卷看上去配置可能不太平民，但是实际上把配置降到60级，然后限定的+4扣掉，也是可以过关的。", "timestamp": "2024-07-14T11:05:00.753000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-15T21:41:00.172000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1262001904179875901", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 228383, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262001903907373147/1262001904179875901/1.jpg?ex=69cbaa5c&is=69ca58dc&hm=b0069cf41e689a9a6eed6b2bfbc552621fed179a2b436baf1b31371868084cea&"}, {"id": "1262001904590786642", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 230677, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262001903907373147/1262001904590786642/2.jpg?ex=69cbaa5c&is=69ca58dc&hm=790d99be52844417cc6289c472ba15f52d27b985459256a91c29c7128da4a962&"}, {"id": "1262001904859218012", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 238402, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262001903907373147/1262001904859218012/3.jpg?ex=69cbaa5c&is=69ca58dc&hm=3786596c6ed87b38797658700e7563576e3c1fe8a0af30488ba88f7130c0e234&"}, {"id": "1262001905257811988", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 232902, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262001903907373147/1262001905257811988/4.jpg?ex=69cbaa5d&is=69ca58dd&hm=42c926a7cad3a835daa6493c6d4c974b3540f3c4c65e797ba2908f4d0f8887db&"}, {"id": "1262001905547087924", "filename": "5.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 240365, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1262001903907373147/1262001905547087924/5.jpg?ex=69cbaa5d&is=69ca58dd&hm=e4c8db60f7023b4bc4f289833bb01bd27175e1842014f7592ef8274426150eaa&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1262001903907373147", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "375攻略指北", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681"]}
